		<title>Naira volatility cost his family. He built an FX platform for businesses.</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/04/17/esca-finance-fx-business/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Emmanuel Nwosu]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 16:25:19 +0000</pubDate>
